---
import BaseLayout from '@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Header from '@/components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '@/components/Footer.astro';

const lastUpdated = 'January 13, 2025';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Now - Alex Rosenkranz"
  description="What I'm up to right now."
>
  <Header />

  <main class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 py-12 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <article class="prose prose-lg dark:prose-invert">
      <h1>What I'm doing now</h1>

      <p class="text-muted-foreground text-sm">
        Last updated: {lastUpdated}
      </p>

      <p>
        This is a <a
          href="https://nownownow.com/about"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer">now page</a
        >—a snapshot of what I'm currently focused on.
      </p>

      <h2>Projects</h2>

      <ul>
        <li>
          <strong>Personal Website Rebuild:</strong> Building this site with Astro,
          Tailwind CSS, and Cloudflare Pages. Implementing a stream-based content
          model for quick posts and longer articles.
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Homelab Setup:</strong> Running Home Assistant and Music Assistant
          on a Raspberry Pi 5, with various Docker services monitored by Datadog.
        </li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Learning</h2>

      <ul>
        <li>Astro framework and static site generation patterns</li>
        <li>Self-hosting services and Linux administration</li>
        <li>Terraform for infrastructure as code</li>
        <li>AWS cloud fundamentals</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Reading</h2>

      <ul>
        <li>Various articles on web performance and observability</li>
        <li>Technical documentation for homelab projects</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Work</h2>

      <p>
        Working at Datadog on observability and developer tools. Focused on
        making complex systems easier to understand and debug.
      </p>

      <hr />

      <p class="text-muted-foreground text-sm">
        Inspired by Derek Sivers' <a
          href="https://nownownow.com"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer">/now</a
        > movement. This page is updated monthly or whenever things change significantly.
      </p>
    </article>
  </main>

  <Footer />
</BaseLayout>
